item.title: CVE-2023-2846|2023-06-30T04:05:26.423Z -- mitsubishi%20electric%20corporation -- melsec-f%20series%20fx3u-16mr%2Fes
item.description: Authentication Bypass by Capture-replay vulnerability in Mitsubishi Electric Corporation MELSEC iQ-F Series main modules allows a remote unauthenticated attacker to cancel the password/keyword setting and login to the affected products by sending specially crafted packets.
